snippet.title: Tobuscus Adventures: WIZARDS Game (LAUNCH TRAILER)
snippet.description:
Tobuscus Adventures: WIZARDS - OUT NOW! ► https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tobuscus-adventures-wizards/id916585802?mt=8
Thank you to everyone who made this possible!! It's finally up, and I think you're going to love it.  It took maybe 8 times longer than we originally had hoped, and we went waayyyy over budget - but IT IS HERE!  Please leave detailed reviews so we can catch any serious bugs in the first patch!  
I'll post another update here soon, and get back on my regular schedule with everything :)  Had to separate from things to completely focus on this game for a while.  Check out my TobyTurner channel for a quick update :) http://youtube.com/tobyturner
BLESS YOUR FACE
